CINTAS will never ask you for your bank account information during the hiring process.

    CINTAS will only communicate with you via phone or email coming from its domain, Cintas.com.  Cintas will not communicate with you via other forms of email or electronic communication such as google, yahoo, hang out, etc.  If you receive communications from these types of sources, you should not give out your personal information and contact Cintas using the contact information provided to verify the accuracy of any messages you receive.
Cintas Corporation is an EEO/Affirmative Action Employer and will make all employment-related decisions without regard to race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, disability or protected veteran status. EEO is the Law. Click here to read more.
* If you are interested in applying for employment with Cintas Corporation and need special assistance or an accommodation to apply for a posted position, call 877-692-3211 to leave a message with your requested accommodation.


    

