The Cintas Uniform Program
Uniforms speak volumes when it comes to maintaining a consistent, professional image for your employees, which is key to attracting guests and differentiating your business from the competition. Uniforms make a positive impact and are what customers expect.

 
Our Heritage
Since 1929, Cintas has grown to clothe more than 5 million people every work day.
Read more

 
The Cintas Distinction
Fortune magazine has listed Cintas among America's Most Admired Companies 9 years!
Read more



 
How It Works
Each week, we pick up your soiled uniforms and deliver professionally cleaned ones...
Read more




Rental Uniforms
With a Cintas full-service uniform rental program, there is no laundry to do, no uniforms to buy, and no repairs or maintenance to waste your time and money — and that means no worries!

 
