Service


Founded
1929; 88 years ago (1929) (as Acme Industrial Laundry Company)
1972 (1972) (as Cintas)


Headquarters
Cincinnati, Ohio, U.S.



Key people

Richard Farmer, Chairman Emeritus; Scott Farmer, CEO; J. Phillip Holloman, President & COO; Robert J. Kohlhepp, Chairman of the Board


Revenue



 US$ 4.905  billion (2016) [1]
 US$ 4.476 billion (2015) [1]






